main event: A UFO observation was recorded on 6 SEP 53, described as an oval object moving rapidly from East to West.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 12 seconds and involved both ground radar and air visual detection., The UFO disappeared behind clouds at an altitude of 4000 feet., No other characteristics of the object could be determined after it disappeared., There were no photographs available with the report., The sighting is included in the Project Blue Book archives.
witness description: Observation from radar and air visual, no specific witnesses recorded.
